bility:\n- **C** is \u201cnot very willing to further his education,\u201d a weakness for future growth, but this is outweighed by his proven crew\u2011cooperation and reliability.\n- The other candidates have no documented strengths in teamwork and have interpersonal issues that could impede long\u2011term crew performance.\nGiven the weighting of the criteria\u2014especially the critical need for effective crew interaction on long\u2011distance routes\u2014**Candidate\u202fC** emerges as the most well\u2011rounded and safest choice despite his modest professional\u2011development weakness.\n**Vote:** Candidate C\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
